    "body": "Tested against all combinations of the following:\r\n\r\n- MHA or MQA/GQA\r\n- causal True or False\r\n- deterministic True or False. 10000 iterations for bitwise equality with determinism \r\n- varlen: cu_seqlens_{q,k} x seqused_{q,k} + maybe zero_lengths_{q,k}\r\n\r\nSpeed looks good for a first version:\r\n\r\n```\r\n### headdim = 192, causal = False, seqlen = 8192, batch_size = 4, nheads = 16, nheads_kv = 16, varlen = False ###\r\nuse_2cta_instrs =  True\r\nFA Python fwd: 1.767ms, 1555.7 TFLOPS\r\nFA Python bwd: 6.406ms, 1072.8 TFLOPS\r\n[deterministic]\r\nFA Python bwd: 6.671ms, 1030.1 TFLOPS\r\n\r\n### headdim = 192, causal = True, seqlen = 8192, batch_size = 4, nheads = 16, nheads_kv = 16, varlen = False ###\r\nuse_2cta_instrs =  True\r\nFA Python fwd: 0.920ms, 1494.1 TFLOPS\r\nFA Python bwd: 3.538ms, 971.1 TFLOPS\r\n[deterministic]\r\nFA Python bwd: 3.813ms, 901.1 TFLOPS\r\n```\r\n\r\nLocal currently disabled for 2cta path, will fix this later along with hdim 128.",
